<h1>Sandra Lima: a inteireza de uma revolucionária proletária</h1>
<p>Author: Movimento Feminino Popular</p>
<p>Time: 2023-03-06T16:38:00-03:00</p>
<p>Images: ['<a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/HO6xXOpj9v6O3qu_VNIJhNCCOGjMV9sagwrLMtGrfGu_BYEAZPCFTlCbz-WTNsG2ALriyElOfWCB1A4=w283-h400">HO6xXOpj9v6O3qu_VNIJhNCCOGjMV9sagwrLMtGrfGu_BYEAZPCFTlCbz-WTNsG2ALriyElOfWCB1A4=w283-h400</a>']</p>
